PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776801953
OL,3,CMental health staff to strike over pay
OL,4,Cdisputes
OL,6,FDrivers will strike from Wednesday 22
OL,7,FApril until Monday 11 May, follows
OL,8,Fwalkouts in January and March.
OL,9,FStriking staff will be on a picket
OL,10,Fline from 7.30am each day at Prestwich
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
