PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776801953
OL,3,CMental health staff to strike over pay
OL,4,Cdisputes
OL,6,FMarc Reed, Director of Capital,
OL,7,FEstates and Facilities at Greater
OL,8,FManchester Mental Health NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust (GMMH), said: "We
OL,10,Fhave been notified by members of
OL,11,FUnison who work as driver porters
OL,12,Fwithin our Transport team that there
OL,13,Fwill be planned industrial action
OL,14,Ftaking place from Tuesday 21 April to
OL,15,FMonday 11 May
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776801953
OL,3,CMental health staff to strike over pay
OL,4,Cdisputes
OL,6,F"Robust plans are in place to minimise
OL,7,Fany disruption to deliveries to and
OL,8,Ffrom services, and the industrial
OL,9,Faction will only involve driver
OL,10,Fporters within GMMH's central
OL,11,FTransport team, based at the Prestwich
OL,12,FSite.
OL,14,F"All other services will operate as
OL,15,Fnormal and actions have been taken to
OL,16,Fprioritise the continuation of
OL,17,Fservices throughout the industrial
OL,18,Faction period.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
