SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776801953
OL,3,CMental health staff to strike over pay
OL,4,Cdisputes
OL,6,F"We remain in active discussions with
OL,7,FUnison and local portering
OL,8,Frepresentatives and continue to work
OL,9,Fconstructively to resolve the dispute."
OL,11,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,12,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,13,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,14,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
